user.biography: Half of the @MyFavoriteMurder podcast and @ExactlyRight podcast network. Obsessed with @ElvisAndMimiAndDot & @OurGirlCookie. Repped by UTA.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Georgia Hardstark on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: Hello! I’m home from treatment! Here’s a selfie! Everything is well with me, and I hope it is with you too! 🥰 #hardstarking

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Georgia Hardstark on July 12, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SUNSHINE HINE SUN'.

node.text:
Hello from Trauma Treatment Summer Camp! I wasn’t sure if I was going to share anything about this, but I’m feeling really incredible and hopeful and so I wanted to spread the love. 
I’ll be here for a few weeks, working on all the stuff that little Georgia in the second pic wasn’t able to at the time. 
If you want to follow along at home, I suggest looking for a therapist that specializes in DBT, and picking up the book Facing Codependency by Pia Melody. 
In the meantime, I’m facing my stuff, focusing on my things, and doing the work! SENDING LOVE!!! xo #hardstarking

node.text: Hiyeee. I’m gonna be off social media for a bit to work on my mental health and everything that comes with it (all positive). Hope you can kind find a moment every day to do the same for yourself! ❤️ #hardstarking

node.text: We decided that this special little guy needed his own special little name. So please, everyone, meet Moses. Aka Moe. 🥰 #heyitsMoe

node.text: Don’t know if I’ll ever be ready to go back to bar-life, but I’ll always be ready for that bathroom-bar-selfie life. #hardstarking #bathroomselfie Cute hair by @hair_o_line!!!

node.text: Love this pic of me and the Cookie Monster, even though she looks a little terrified. I swear she likes being held. #ourgirlcookie #hardstarking

node.text: #ElvisJunior 🥰 Life’s feeling a little hectic right now in good ways and bad, so sorry that I haven’t updated you guys on this adorable thing, but more to come. In the meantime, he’s the sweetest most gentle little baby I’ve ever met, the cats are pissed, and cookie is really really really excited. #heyitsMoe

May be an image of 6 people, people standing and text that says 'SAT 6/26 7:30 PM PST COMEDY SHOW BENEFIT $10 To WATCH THE LIVESTREAM MARY IFY NWADIWE THURMAN ELIZABETH ELLIS NICCOLE GEORGIA HARDSTARK hostedky ATSUKO & DANA OKATSUKA GOULD TICKETS @ VIDIOTSFOUNDATION.ORG/COMEDY'.

node.text:
When I got asked to preform at this fundraiser, I almost cried a little. It feels like I’m being accepted by the cool kids in school. But the kind of cool kids that are super smart, very inclusive, and go to the wackiest events (like turtle races and impromptu plays in the park or something). 

Anyway, I’ll be reading a story from #SSDGM this Saturday. Please come or livestream if you want/can! #myfavoritemurder #hardstarking 

Repost from @vidiots
•
Get them tix pals, link in bio! You need this laugh, and we need your support! Big, gushy, fangurl THANKS to this amazing lineup, @atsukocomedy , @danagould , @niccolethurman , @meellisday , @ifynwadiwe , and @hardstark we 💕 you big time!! Mad respect and appreciation to @heather_hanford for the 🔥 artwork!

node.text: My dad says “everyday is Father’s Day when your grown kids want you in their life.” I know this is a hard day for many people, so I’ll just say this: find a father or father figure, or whatever, who unabashedly reps yours and your husband’s podcast. In fact, borrow mine, America’s Dad, if you’re in need of that figure. #AMERICASDAD #MARTY #murderino #myfavoriteMARTY #ssdgm

#FBF What can I say about my cousin, Dr. Dan [aka cousin Danny], that hasn’t already been said? He’s a mensch of the highest order. One of my favorite cousins to follow around as a kid and force to play with me, which he always did. A wonderful father and husband to one of the kindest families I know. An incredibly smart, kind, empathetic fellow-#Gemini that I am so honored to have as a podcasting partner. 

I’m also SO incredibly proud of the premiere episode of his podcast for the network. We had the most lovely, healing, helpful conversation about reparenting oneself and it’s even helped to mend my relationship with my mom, if you can believe it. 

So please give it a listen, #RateReviewSubscibe (let’s make it go ALL THE WAY TO THE TOP!!!) and check out the MANY past episodes he’s so lovingly crafted over the years. Parents and future-parents, aunties and uncles, friends of parents, and grown kids themselves will all get something out of it, trust me. ❤️❤️❤️#hardstarking 
Repost from @parentfootprintpodcast
•
It’s here! Welcome to the debut episode of Parent Footprint with Dr. Dan on @exactlyright. Today’s guest is Georgia Hardstark (@hardstark) co-host of the true crime and comedy podcast My Favorite Murder @myfavoritemurder and co-founder of the Exactly Right network.  Dr. Dan and Georgia, who are cousins (!!!), give insight into their family, discuss Georgia's openness about her mental health, explain reparenting, and much more (including a few surprises!). Thank you for listening and thanks to our new fam Georgia, Karen, and Exactly Right!

.
